Class Officer

java.lang.Object
entities.User
entities.Applicant
entities.Officer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Filter
public class Officer extends Applicant
The Officer class represents a user with officer privileges who can manage and register for HDB projects. It extends the Applicant class, inheriting its basic properties and adding additional features specific to the Officer role, such as project management and enquiry handling.
